{"abstract": "In many real-world applications of machine learning classifiers, it is essential to predict the probability of an example belonging to a particular class. This paper proposes a simple technique for predicting probabilities based on optimizing a ranking loss, followed by isotonic regression. This semi-parametric technique offers both good ranking and regression performance, and models a richer set of probability distributions than statistical workhorses such as logistic regression. We provide experimental results that show the effectiveness of this technique on real-world applications of probability prediction.", "referenced_work_ids": ["93d0b2971e95a581031059ee4b2af0705644321b", "e3285873053d93d9c375747a335dd874de76ab77", "2a6cac2931f0e44edb37cdf41d02b9b9aea729fa", "2c0c475448259887c42cac4571ad8bc44410cfa7", "7ce72ae1502c05712213f13d2407488e462120d8", "b7708a5cd608a87cba87b41cffecb3b8db9445ea", "d1454e3823501a8ee9fe97250c5b0c9cfc690153", "1d844bb8b556a795115144e0264b44d7f68b841a", "76188dba4c840c638642cdbaa8fb196ec83cac16", "505253630ab7e8f35e26e27904bd3c8faea3c5ce", "427b168f490b56716f22b129ac93aba5425ea08f", "014986ade7e67cb8d45f039796ce4bcfbab75f4d", "08ab0660cae082b524aabb1ffa9c5a53deb09da5", "eae3948747c9d051314c1f5851957b833aa83eca", "7678da8b2eb70a5383f203d948564d8f48c0c62a", "04e10f745a7267453788a22f5150b5a32b2b3951", "cfd4259d305a00f13d5f08841230389f61322422", "4b0e8659e4a477d4e1559ebd052b69fb7a0e7eab", "d33c6d671580bc5104db395c4004370c7c299db3", "68dae4dfa9021d32ac89cface5956464e5e0bd51", "746e1c10ca4af0f736682dda3c967d371eeb086c", "c586d33e1b0c71970bd876649b9f3d8f0b2341e0", "de083d106c783cd55d0611213467a932e0971879", "644637257ff5430f18cf228a8723c43ab0186eae", "eab3ba9b979bcc77143059255221f7ba9a0fe9fe", "245286ad2226648c201712a5f86124e2d668a3c4", "c74f3c797a2238d0a40fdce8dd201789bbc1242a", "73c048e02fb66320fc48b893577262862fd74b5f", "69777bb0d810ffb40b120b939a892ab93c72a8fe", "05713da3bd396fef9611761fab4d88a21671ca43", "d6706b6e626c15680688b